prodNameC: 岱安韶韻總甲狀腺素125I放射免疫分析試劑組
prodNameE: DiaSorin Clinical Assays GammaCoat M Total T4 125I  RIA kit
ingredientsDesc:
1. 125I Thyroxine Tracer Cat. No. CA-2635. 1/5 per kit. Each vial contains approximately 5 μCi tracer (<1 μg/ml T4) in 10 ml of tris buffered saline with 0.1% sodium azide as a preservative.
2. Anti-T4 Coated Tubes (Mouse Monoclonal) Cat. No. CA-2173. 100/500 per/kit. 12 x 75 mm tubes are coated with anti-T4 mouse monoclonal antibody (titer <1 μg/tube) and packaged in a plastic bag.
3. T4 Reagent Buffer Concentrate (11x) Cat. No. CA-2736. 1/5 per kit. Each vial contains 10 ml of tris buffered saline, 4 mM ANS, 6 mM sodium salicylate with 0.2% sodium azide as a preservative.
4. T4 Serum Blank Cat. No. CA-2280. 1/1 per kit. Each vial contains 1 ml of processed human serum with 0.1% sodium azide as a preservative.
5. T4 Serum Standards Cat. No. CA-2281, CA-2285.1/1 per/kit. Each vial contains L-thyroxine in 1 ml of processed human serum with 0.1% sodium azide as a preservative. Standards are provided at the following total T4 concentrations: 1, 4, 8, 12 & 20 μg/dl, respectively.
6. Auxiliary Labels For trac
applicantAddr: 台北市中正區忠孝西路一段50號18樓之2
efficacy: 以放射免疫分析法定量檢測血清中甲狀腺素之濃度。
